Description: Color library for Python
 ColorAide is a pure Python, object-oriented color library that provides
 a wide range of color spaces and color manipulation features.
 .
 Features include:
  - Support for many color spaces (sRGB, Display P3, Lab, LCH, Oklab, etc.)
  - Color conversion between spaces
  - Color mixing and interpolation
  - Color difference calculations (Delta E)
  - CSS color parsing and formatting
  - Color harmonies and manipulation
